Read `AGENTS.md` first.

Treat `docs/` as the long-term source of truth for product behavior, architecture, and workflow.
Read `CONTRIBUTING.md` before preparing a pull request.

If you change behavior, update `docs/product.md`.
If you change structure, update `docs/architecture.md`.
Run `make check` before `make test`.
